      %p== Running is great exercise. And, let's face itâ€”programmers aren't known for getting a lot of exercise. So take this opportunity to get some! If you can't run 3.1 miles yet, it's a nice attainable distance if you start training now.  We recommend the #{link_to "Couch-to-5k", "http://www.coolrunning.com/engine/2/2_3/181.shtml"} program.

